Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:17.40,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}似てても違うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:20.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}マンダリン　オレンジ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:24.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}友達　恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:28.16,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}２人のココロも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:31.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}傷つきたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:34.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私は逃げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:37.90,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そしたら光も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:41.95,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}射してはくれない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.84,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡なのにね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:48.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}出逢いも恋も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:51.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}種もつぼみも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:59.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ青い　実でさえも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:02.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}オレンジ色は　あの日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:04.08,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}見た夕焼けを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:07.37,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出させてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:09.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}２つの影が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:14.31,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}手を繋いでるみたいだった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:16.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}オレンジ　いつか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:17.85,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}甘くなるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:21.12,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}それともしぼんじゃうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:24.58,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私の未来知りたくなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:27.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ぜんぶ食べた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:30.40,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}すっぱい…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:38.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好きだけど泣けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:45.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}オレンジ色に　早く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:46.95,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}なりたい果実
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:50.24,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}キミの光を浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:53.75,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}理想や夢は膨らむばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:57.03,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}気づいてよ　ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:21:59.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}オレンジ　今日も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:00.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}食べてみたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:03.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}まだすっぱくて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:07.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私みたいで残せないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:13.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ぜんぶ食べた　好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:16.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}すっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.86,0:22:23.42,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}泣けるよ　好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:25.11,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好きだよ
